---
---
<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0a1628] via-[#0d2137] to-[#0a2a40] text-white flex flex-col items-center text-center px-[6%] py-24">
  <!-- Glow effects -->
  <div class="absolute -top-52 -left-36 w-[700px] h-[700px] rounded-full bg-purple-700/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-40 -right-24 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full bg-cyan-500/10 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

  <span class="relative inline-block bg-cyan-500/10 border border-cyan-500/30 text-cyan-300 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full mb-6">
    🚀 Aplicaciones web para negocios reales
  </span>

  <h1 class="relative text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight max-w-3xl">
    Tu negocio,
    <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-300 to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent"> digitalizado</span><br/>
    en tiempo récord
  </h1>

  <p class="relative mt-5 text-lg text-blue-300 max-w-xl">
    Desarrollamos aplicaciones web simples, rápidas y económicas para talleres mecánicos, peluquerías caninas, gimnasios y muchos rubros más.
  </p>

  <div class="relative mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center">
    <a
      href="#rubros"
      class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600 to-cyan-500 text-white font-bold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,180,216,0.4)] hover:opacity-90 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
    >
      Ver rubros disponibles
    </a>
    <a
      href="#contacto"
      class="border-2 border-cyan-500 text-cyan-300 font-bold px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full hover:bg-cyan-500/10 hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition-all"
    >
      Hablar con un asesor
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
